<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.10">
<l>paruntāṭ kaḷiṟṟuk karuḷceyta paramaṉ ṟaṉṉaip pāriṉmēl</l>
<l>viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭamai viṭṭu cittaṉ kōtaicol</l>
<l>maruntā meṉṟu tammaṉattē vaittuk koṇṭu vāḻvārkaḷ</l>
<l>peruntā ḷuṭaiya pirāṉaṭikkīḻp piriyā teṉṟu miruppārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who live by keeping in their minds that the words of Kōtai</l>
<l>[daughter of] Viṣṇucitta, about [her] seeing—in Bṛndāvana on this earth—</l>
<l>the Supreme Being who bestowed grace upon the thicked-legged male elephant</l>
<l>will always remain unparted from beneath the feet of the Lord with great feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
